but he's in no present danger.

05:05.236 --> 05:08.340
<i>We consider his condition
to be satisfactory.</i>

05:08.406 --> 05:11.843
Is Reinhardt acting as
an INDIVIDUAL or as a member
of a terrorist group?

05:11.910 --> 05:14.479
