to give medical information.

05:22.454 --> 05:25.357
Could you give us the name
of the victim-- The woman
that you're treating?

05:25.423 --> 05:27.525
Yes. Her name is
Katherine Mcallister.

05:27.592 --> 05:30.362
She's 32 years old.
She's from minneapolis,
minnesota.

05:30.428 --> 05:33.531
- What's her status?
