in reviving her vital signs.

05:52.817 --> 05:55.320
Dr. Samuels.

05:55.387 --> 05:59.124
Did you actually bring
Katherine Mcallister
back from the dead?

05:59.190 --> 06:03.128
Well, uh, in a clinical sense,
I suppose you can say
that's True, Yeah.

06:03.194 --> 06:05.563
Have you been involved
in Cases such
as this before?

06:05.630 --> 06:08.166
Yes, I have.
This, uh--

06:13.338 --> 06:15.707
Actually, uh, Dr. Craig...

06:15.774 --> 06:18.910
