hemorrhage.

06:27.419 --> 06:29.921
How long did you
operate on her, Dr. Craig?

06:29.988 --> 06:33.525
In point of fact,
I was not the surgeon
of record.

06:33.591 --> 06:35.894
But as department chairman
of surgery,

06:35.960 --> 06:39.097
