excuse me.

10:35.100 --> 10:38.703
Mr. Broadwater,
how are we this morning?
Feeling pretty Good.

10:38.770 --> 10:41.473
Well, I have some good news
and I have some bad.

10:41.539 --> 10:45.410
Two of the major vessels to
your heart, the left anterior
descending artery...

10:45.477 --> 10:50.482
