Mr. Broadwater. What does
this look like to you?

11:13.638 --> 11:16.441
A rubber tube.
Arteries are tubes.

11:16.508 --> 11:20.578
They carry the blood
and oxygen from the heart.
Now, bear with me.

11:20.645 --> 11:24.749
If we obstruct the flow of blood
and oxygen to the brain,

11:24.816 --> 11:27.352
what do you think happens?

11:27.419 --> 11:30.488
