your knee, or if you're lucky,
when you're sleeping.

11:47.072 --> 11:50.275
Oh, my dear God.

11:50.342 --> 11:54.346
Now for the good news.
I'm going to save you.

11:54.412 --> 11:56.548
How?
Triple Bypass.

11:56.614 --> 11:59.517
Surgery?

11:59.584 --> 12:02.854
We'll give you a few moments
to think about it,
notify your loved ones.

12:02.921 --> 12:06.191
Do I have your complete
cooperation?

12:06.257 --> 12:08.793
I guess so.

12:08.860 --> 12:10.829
Excellent.

12:14.799 --> 12:16.801
What's the matter, Lavine?

12:16.868 --> 12:19.904
