Now, I'm going to read out
the class list.

37:13.131 --> 37:15.867
Please raise your hand
when I call out your name.

37:15.934 --> 37:18.036
Julie Seltzer.

37:19.170 --> 37:21.473
Hugh Beale.

37:21.539 --> 37:24.676
Right here, ma'am.

37:26.211 --> 37:30.015
You're Hugh Beale?
Yes, ma'am.
Present and accounted for.

37:37.789 --> 37:41.960
The fundamental problem
is that cops carry guns,
not hypodermics, and--

37:42.027 --> 37:44.596
<i>[ pager BEEPING ]</i>

37:50.902 --> 37:54.839
so, you choked.
I almost wet my pants--
My paper Pants.

37:54.906 --> 37:57.142
Craig's evaluating me.
He thinks I'm an idiot.

37:57.208 --> 37:59.711
You better spit it out
when you're trailing him
in post-Op.

37:59.778 --> 38:02.414
I feel sick
just thinking about it.

38:13.825 --> 38:16.061
Morning, Morrison.
Dr. Westphall.

38:24.669 --> 38:29.341
Well, if it isn't
the good samaritan.

38:29.407 --> 38:33.645
I'm changing rotations.
Another Resident's gonna
be taking care of you.

38:35.280 --> 38:37.682
Did you come down here
to tell me that?

38:37.749 --> 38:39.818
No.

38:49.027 --> 38:51.997
[ Machine BEEPING ]

39:09.781 --> 39:11.683
Katherine Mcallister.

39:12.784 --> 39:14.853
<i>She was in the bank.</i>

39:18.923 --> 39:21.893
[ sighs ]

39:29.801 --> 39:33.104
<i>What was that all about?
Was I supposed to
feel something, Morrison?</i>

39:33.171 --> 39:36.508
What do you feel?
You mean legally
or in my soul?

39:36.574 --> 39:40.745
Legally, it was an accident.
In my soul, none of
your damn business.

39:42.747 --> 39:45.583
I've got so much anger
towards you,

39:45.650 --> 39:48.420
and it hasn't made
for good doctoring.

39:48.486 --> 39:52.324
I know you say you believe
in something, that you did
this for a reason.

39:52.390 --> 39:56.628
I know that.
But what you've done...

39:56.695 --> 39:59.364
is a chilling perversion
of everything human.

40:02.267 --> 40:06.237
You're privileged,
Reinhardt. You've been
handed everything.

40:06.304 --> 40:08.373
Why?

40:08.440 --> 40:10.575
Why'd you do it?

40:12.444 --> 40:14.846
You're soft.

40:14.913 --> 40:18.350
You're weak.
You wouldn't understand.

40:25.223 --> 40:27.125
No.

40:28.793 --> 40:30.729
No, I guess not.

40:33.798 --> 40:36.267
Take him back
to his room.

